<h2>What comes after the coming soon landing page?</h2>
<p>The coming soon pageâ€”in case it wasnâ€™t obviousâ€”is the very beginning of the relationship between you and your customer.Â You donâ€™t just set up a coming soon page and call it a day. The point Is to attract interest, increase brand awareness, get new email subscribers, and more.</p>
