<p>A coming soon page ought to get you some information from your customer. In this day and age, ideally youâ€™ll get an email address. You want an email list of potential customers: <a href="https://www.salecycle.com/blog/stats/18-essential-email-marketing-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">59%</a> of customers said email marketing has motivated them to make a purchase.</p>
