<li><strong>Have only one form to fill out</strong>. Streamline the process and ask only for whatâ€™s most importantâ€”the customerâ€™s email.</li>
<li><strong>Set a countdown</strong>. If you donâ€™t want a physical countdown timer on your page, thatâ€™s fine. Just mention in the copy a general idea of when youâ€™re launching.</li>
