<div>
<div class="video-embed-field-provider-youtube video-embed-field-responsive-video"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yrxOOK-U4Uw?autoplay=0&amp;start=0&amp;rel=0" width="854" height="480" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<p>But personalized videos donâ€™t need to be this complicated. They can be as simple as listing, at the very beginning of the video, â€œThis video was made specifically for [Customer Name], who wants to [complete a buying action].â€</p>
<p>By including this personalized intro, now the rest of the video feels personal,Â too.</p>
<h3>Benefits of personalized videos in your marketing strategy</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.wyzowl.com/video-marketing-statistics-2019/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">87%</a> of businesses use video as a marketing tool, so it makes sense that 90% of video marketers feel â€œthe level of competition and noise has increased.â€</p>
<p>But what are the benefits of personalized marketing?</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="1d8402ef-497a-4928-9fbb-04dbf539c7a9" data-langcode="en">
