										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The average conversion rate for ecommerce sites is <a href="https://www.invespcro.com/blog/the-average-website-conversion-rate-by-industry/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2.63%</a></p>
<p>Let that sink in.</p>
<div class="embedded-entity align-center" data-embed-button="images" data-entity-embed-display="view_mode:media.simple_image" data-entity-type="media" data-entity-uuid="7b470a94-7fc7-491c-93f4-c2ab4e958c54" data-langcode="en">
