<h2>Optimize your entire ecommerce sales funnel</h2>
<p>Mapping your customerâ€™s journey to the ecommerce funnel is a great way to recalibrate your digital marketing strategies.</p>
<p>Too often we see jarring changes between building awareness and increasing consideration. This disunity in an ecommerce strategy can hurt your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2019/08/19/conversion-rate-benchmarks">conversion rates</a>, but by creating marketing strategies with your sales funnel in mind, you can create a seamless journey that works to propel your potential customer into not only an existing customer but a returning customer.</p>
