					<description><![CDATA[<p>This post covers how to use your analytics and audience insights to identify the best times to run Facebook ads for your businessâ€”plus a refresher on ad types and budgeting tips.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/03/19/best-time-to-run-facebook-ads">Best Time to Run Facebook Ads? Look at Your Own Data</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
